<template>
  {{ mini }}
</template>

<script>
import { reactive } from '@vue/reactivity'
export default {
    name: 'RedditListItem',
    props: ['item',],
    setup() {

      const mini = reactive({
        title: item.title,
        thumbnail: item.thumbnail,
      })

      return { mini }
    }
    
}
</script>
